}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "RTA7158W-D61-REV1" is silkscreened on the main board.
===Specifications=== *[http://www.natthapol89.com/2014/04/asus-dsl-n10-a1.html ''Asus DSL-N10 A1 Review'' on '''natthapol'''] :Router CPU: [[Ralink]] RT3050F @320MHz WiSoC :Router RAM: [[Winbond]] W9825G6JH-6 32MB (SDRAM) :Router Flash: ''Macronix'' MX25L3206EM2I-12G 4MB (SPI) :ADSL CPU: [[TrendChip]] TC3162LE-LQ128G (ADSL2+ Annex A) :ADSL RAM: [[Winbond]] W9816G6IH-6 2MB (SDRAM) :ADSL Flash: ''Macronix'' MX25L8006EM2I-12G 1MB (SPI) :ADSL Chip: [[TrendChip]] TC3086-QFN64-EPG
===Models=== *[[ASUS DSL-N10]] rev A1 • OEM: [[Askey]] RTA7156W-D61 REV6 :[[TrendChip]] TC3162LE/RT3050F, Flash: W25Q32BVSIG (4MB) *[[ASUS DSL-N10 rev B1]] • OEM: [[Askey]] RTA7158W-D61 REV1 :[[TrendChip]] TC3162LE-LQ128G, Flash: W25Q32BV • [https://remont-aud.net/dump/planshety_i_ehl_knigi/asus/asus_asus_dsl_n10_shassi_main_board_rta7158w_d61_rev1/464-1-0-118148 FW] *[[ASUS DSL-N10 rev C1]] (with 5dBi antenna) • [https://www.asus.com/Networking/DSLN10_C1/ PPage] :[[Ralink]] RT63365/RT5390; Flash: 8MB, RAM: 32MB (DDR)
